  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ahem~</i> “Looks like yet another unlucky warlock has stumbled straight into a 1600°C alchemy furnace!” “Welcome to <i>Alchemage</i>! That’s right—you’ve just stepped into a sandbox action-adventure world.”</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Sandbox Building】This is the Age of Magic, not the age of farming, you muggle! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > To get rich, start by chopping trees! No axe, no pickaxe needed—just raise your magic staff, aim at whatever you want to dismantle, and <i>zzzzap</i>—you’ll collect all kinds of resource blocks. Simple enough, right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/5a92c13a41088c41efd525725d1fbd56.poster.avif?t=1772793206\" width=1000 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/5a92c13a41088c41efd525725d1fbd56.webm?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/5a92c13a41088c41efd525725d1fbd56.mp4?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/d7903a5121f5bd3d3347635453d12031.poster.avif?t=1772793206\" width=1000 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/d7903a5121f5bd3d3347635453d12031.webm?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/d7903a5121f5bd3d3347635453d12031.mp4?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, a clever one like you must be itching to bash some monster skulls with it—I won’t stop you~ But I’d recommend a far better way ↓</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Magical Battle】Summon wind and rain, command thunder and lightning—the era of true power has come, Master! — <i>Combat Styles & Characteristic Magic</i> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Still hacking away with a dragon-slaying sword? Still taking aim with a little pistol? Those old-fashioned weapons are too weak. Try blasting your enemies’ heads with magic instead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/587b6c22f8b05ddd717c0a0bb8541068.poster.avif?t=1772793206\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/587b6c22f8b05ddd717c0a0bb8541068.webm?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/587b6c22f8b05ddd717c0a0bb8541068.mp4?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlike weapon systems in similar games, the core power here lies in the four elemental alchemy magics: <i>Water, Fire, Earth, and Wind.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whoa—s-so it was about roasting monsters? Whmmm<i>...</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each element interacts differently with the environment and creatures. Go explore this world and collect more magic scrolls to unlock their full potential~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/2162da829734bce1038ab34e7ae07f5d.poster.avif?t=1772793206\" width=1000 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/2162da829734bce1038ab34e7ae07f5d.webm?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/2162da829734bce1038ab34e7ae07f5d.mp4?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Survival Challenge】But at the end of the day, survival comes first. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A little vest won’t stop the arrows of a skeleton archer, and monsters won’t wait around for you to “grow strong”! Build yourself a quick shelter or design a luxurious otherworldly villa, patch together some leather armor or weave a cozy fur coat—keeping yourself alive and well is the top priority~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/43839a70c82a04f718bd003336118b13.poster.avif?t=1772793206\" width=1000 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/43839a70c82a04f718bd003336118b13.webm?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/43839a70c82a04f718bd003336118b13.mp4?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/55d6a567942a197ab7836fea54aa4abe.poster.avif?t=1772793206\" width=1000 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/55d6a567942a197ab7836fea54aa4abe.webm?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/55d6a567942a197ab7836fea54aa4abe.mp4?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【<i>Multiplayer Support</i>】Life in another world can get lonely alone—but what about four people? </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game supports up to four players online, with both PvE and PvP! Not that I’d ever tell you that you can summon your friends into the world of <i>Alchemage</i> together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/225ffd9cfb6f13beb99a727933297dec.poster.avif?t=1772793206\" width=1000 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/225ffd9cfb6f13beb99a727933297dec.webm?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/225ffd9cfb6f13beb99a727933297dec.mp4?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Finally, welcome to <i>Alchemage</i>!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlucky Alchemist, kick off your adventure! Along the way, rare materials, spooky creatures, and powerful alchemy magic are all waiting for you to discover and collect. We believe you have what it takes to unravel the mysteries hidden deep within this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/b3cac3b5ae7c87be6257d6d42d0afbea.poster.avif?t=1772793206\" width=1000 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/b3cac3b5ae7c87be6257d6d42d0afbea.webm?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/691390/extras/b3cac3b5ae7c87be6257d6d42d0afbea.mp4?t=1772793206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
